      <section name="Welcome to Holodeck">
      <p>
        Holodeck is a software for B2B Messaging, based on the following
        <a href="http://www.oasis-open.org">Oasis</a> specifications: ebXML Messaging version 3 and AS4 Profile.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can find out more information in the "About Holodeck"
        section of the navigation. This includes an in-depth description of
        <a href="what-is-holodeck.html">what Holodeck is</a>,
        a <a href="holodeck-features.html">list of some of its main features</a>,
        and a set of <a href="general.html">frequently
        asked questions about what Holodeck is</a>.
      </p>

